    "title": "Vanilla — Standard 3-Bedroom Family Home",
    "summary": "Baseline visual test case. Generous 14m × 22m suburban lot (308 sqm) with a straightforward 11-room brief. Program fits comfortably inside the buildable envelope. Intended to settle quickly and produce multiple accepted candidates.",
